Direct/Ice Bash/Shove a Piece 1 tile, freezing it as well if it's an Enemy. If the shoved Piece lands on another Piece, deal 4 damage to the Piece if it's an Enemy, and damage the Piece if it's a Hero. Shoving a Piece off the left, right, and top of the map kills it.

Indirect/Frostbringer/After moving to a tile, all Enemies along the same horizontal line as the Frost Knight are frozen. 